TRON2 Gazebo / ROS simulation
Copyright (c) 2024-2026 LimX Dynamics Inc.

This product bundles a Gazebo hardware-simulation plugin
(`tron2_gazebo`) and a simulation-side C++ SDK (`limxsdk-sim`) that
bridges the plugin to the TRON2 SDK RobotCmd / RobotState API used by
downstream control code.

